description:
A basic 101 introduction to the Physics.

Updated quality of the content based on customer feedback.

Includes:

Physics,
Matter,
Motion,
Force,
Dynamics,
Gravitation,
Relativity,
Wave and Light,
Heat and Temperature,
Thermodynamics,
Electricity and Magnetism,
Radioactivity,
Physical Constants,
Units,
Dimensional Analysis,
Formula Pack 01,
Formula Pack 02,
Formula Pack 03.

Also added search based on customer feedback.


Please write to us. We would love to improve this app
